Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家這麼晚還在外面遊蕩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.47,0:01:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  必須得懲罰一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.91,0:01:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.55,0:01:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使不是已經不會傷害我們了的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.09,0:02:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.40,0:02:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙不是奏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.36,0:02:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏是不會對毫無抵抗的我們進行攻擊的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.43,0:02:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游離子  我們要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  以半圓形圍住她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.51,0:02:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行集中攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:24.64,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是你這傢伙在發號施令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.79,0:02:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被distortion擋開  也不要停下攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:25.95,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.17,0:02:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.10,0:02:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.51,0:02:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快閃開  由理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.36,0:02:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.23,0:02:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏她不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼深的傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.35,0:02:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是致命傷也會很快好起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣的傢伙居然有兩個  到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.71,0:03:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界什麼時候變得這麼莫名其妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是有緣由的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得天使領域入侵作戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她的電腦裡不是有一個開發技能的軟體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡面有幾個從未見過的技能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.91,0:03:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是其中一個叫「harmonics」的技能發動了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「harmonics」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.98,0:03:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個什麼樣的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當時沒看畫面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是把一個身體分裂成兩個的技能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是分身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.81,0:03:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說這也是天使自己用軟體開發的技能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但感覺並非是完全相同的兩個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.09,0:03:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這傢伙不同  很好戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.25,0:03:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏她只使用保護自己的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用刀刃時也一樣  只是為了擋住子彈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.52,0:03:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你們這群廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:04:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  音無同學除外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為笨蛋基本都聚集在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我告訴你們其中一個可能性好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假設那個分身的產生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在擁有強烈的攻擊意志的時候的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.84,0:04:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說分身一直遵從著當時本體的命令嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.35,0:04:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  奏不可能擁有強烈的攻擊意志
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這無所謂  不過你好像很護著她嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為  她很可憐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  現在的問題是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和天使的分身戰鬥的方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  是消除方法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:47.27,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙在幹什麼  快放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  如果分身是因為她的意志而產生的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.06,0:04:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也應該能用她的意志來消除吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只需要等她醒來不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  如果能用意志消除的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她還會躺在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:05:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是無意識下的產物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以連她也無法消除
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算同歸於盡也只好拼命上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.48,0:05:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.26,0:05:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙不會消失的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豈不是要一直在這個世界存在下去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在放過了我們  但明天開始應該不會了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦偏離規範行為  恐怕會立刻和昨天一樣變成一場血戰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不是學生會長？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  因為她完全繼承了約束我們的那份意志
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上生性好戰  糟糕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算想反抗也沒有時間去準備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些時間要怎樣去爭取
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去上課  並裝作聽課的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不能去聽老師講課的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認真上課的話就會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不被分身發現的情況下幹別的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且堅持一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.07,0:06:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望下次再見的時候  不要少了任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.24,0:07:01.29,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\pos(575,250)}女生宿舍  天使領域
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:07:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我知道可以分身啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒辦法讓另一個消失嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.51,0:07:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Angel  Player...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軟體的使用手冊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  這麼厚一本還全是英語
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就沒什麼時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.38,0:07:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  跳高了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.43,0:07:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是距離嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒意義
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.66,0:07:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來是連上這個指令就會自動消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那它的發動條件是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆把整個電腦都破壞掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡嗎  那分身就不會消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  直接改寫成我能明白的程式算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.47,0:07:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間限制是10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10秒鐘要等起來還真是漫長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.93,0:08:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼就不能設置到10秒以下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算是搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增加了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「howling」？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.39,0:08:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是分身做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要刪除掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.35,0:08:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了  都做得這麼周密了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須盡可能少修改一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.09,0:08:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下只要她再使用一次「harmonics」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「absorb」這個技能就會發動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身就會回到本體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失策了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她自己出去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:08:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏和我約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會和我們在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.83,0:09:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做過那種約定了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.28,0:09:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這副凌亂的樣子肯定是被綁走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.66,0:09:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙到底做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.81,0:09:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我改寫了程式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要她再使用一次那個力量的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追加能力就會發動  分身就應該會回到本體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.69,0:09:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事也能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臨陣磨槍而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是敵人的行動比預想的還快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她被藏起來的話就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.08,0:09:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能去找了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要一邊躲避兇惡的天使嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是假裝上課就已經夠麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.84,0:09:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佯攻到底能撐多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.96,0:09:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佯攻是說我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是為了什麼加入GDM的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.15,0:09:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為崇拜岩澤同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.14,0:09:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GDM可是為了佯攻而存在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  面對那麼可怕的對手怎麼佯攻呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.77,0:09:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你佯攻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.13,0:09:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為你誰呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.91,0:09:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡我可是你的前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:09:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼反倒是你發火了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:10:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩嗎  真是對不起了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  雖然在演唱會中可能會尿褲子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不會退縮的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.42,0:10:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份決心先謝謝你了  不過現在還不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先去做力所能及的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.74,0:10:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳達給所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集目擊到天使的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.58,0:10:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey  yo!  Check  this  out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.40,0:10:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a moonwalk, it's a moonwalk... Headspin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.44,0:10:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛收集來的情報看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囚禁的場所很可能是在Guild
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.71,0:10:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  一定是在那最底層
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個爆破掉的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.97,0:10:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  陷阱也還開啟著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最為危險  距離這裡最遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.30,0:10:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要潛入這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.51,0:10:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次可幾乎是全滅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在怕什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是第一個死的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了大家我即使尿褲子也會繼續唱下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展現出自己的毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對那種對手  佯攻也是等著被秒殺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次不需要佯攻  堂堂正正地去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.04,0:10:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要兼顧和天使的戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.19,0:11:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰內容是空降至Guild
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在其最底層順利奪回天使的本體
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.11,0:11:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:28.88,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild聯絡通道  B4
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.42,0:11:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的陷阱擱著沒人管  真幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.47,0:11:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…在這裡碰上天使的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是會尿褲子的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.74,0:11:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.27,0:11:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請有所謂啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.42,0:11:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請有所謂啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼快就出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.99,0:11:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  好快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.63,0:11:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有手槍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.26,0:11:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guard  Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「distortion」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.68,0:12:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會比預想的更快搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.98,0:12:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.81,0:12:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙也是分身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.12,0:12:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼還有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就是敵人又增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣  那傢伙又是第一個被幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.65,0:12:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背後的要怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.41,0:12:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是想這個的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.01,0:12:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先對付眼前的這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您似乎很忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游離子  快沒子彈了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.73,0:12:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去封住路口  跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.84,0:12:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:12:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能趕上的人就留下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.60,0:13:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.56,0:13:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.57,0:13:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.54,0:13:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.62,0:13:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.71,0:13:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.77,0:13:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:19.29,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild聯絡通道  B5
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼凶暴的天使居然有兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比上次空降作戰的處境還要糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.68,0:13:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會出現第二個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身都使出「handsonic」和「distortion」了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.90,0:13:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說「harmonics」也能使用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.15,0:13:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們真是一群低能兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  音無同學除外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來總結問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼有請
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.65,0:13:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題有兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是究竟製造了多少個分身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.73,0:13:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果分身能製造分身的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那數量就沒有限制了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那別說是兩個了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十個…二十個  說不定還有更多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但由理已經追加過技能了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.72,0:14:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身是會回到本體的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要等她們消失不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是第二個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.14,0:14:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在那能力追加以前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.35,0:14:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身就已經量產了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚民們  終於注意到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  音無同學是高貴的貴族
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.61,0:14:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她知道我們會潛入這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並把已經量產了的分身佈置在這個Guild的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,trap
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,0:14:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  這是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背後已經有兩個了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們不會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們毫無勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.79,0:14:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這前方…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也聚集了很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說被困在這裡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.80,0:14:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連武器也沒法補給
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是等著被幹掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出這種事到底有什麼目的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就結果而言是讓我們完全服從吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:14:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是她的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們老老實實地消失嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.76,0:15:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個把我們一網打盡的絕妙作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:25.95,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild聯絡通道  B10
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再…浪費子彈了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松下五段！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.98,0:15:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走  趁我還有意識的時候快走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.91,0:15:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  這種好像只有在臨死時才是條好漢的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點  趁現在快走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.52,0:15:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撐住啊  松下五段
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.64,0:15:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面就交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.54,0:15:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:16:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓松下君白白犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:04.29,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild聯絡通道  B11
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.07,0:16:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托他的福我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.95,0:16:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要前進那是最好的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.33,0:16:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為天使身體比較小
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要封住她的動作的話  那樣做是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.66,0:16:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管天使有多麼大的力氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柔道的固技對她都會有效
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.40,0:16:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松下君教我們的柔道終於有實用的一天了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說對付一個天使只要犧牲一個人就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犧牲就行了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.69,0:16:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後只要我們能救出本體  他們也都能獲救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.17,0:16:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:36.41,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild聯絡通道  B12
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's  my  turn
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get  chance  and  luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TK
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.62,0:16:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  什麼啊  這種像少年漫畫最終回一樣的劇情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管了  繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.04,0:16:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展現這身肌肉的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高松
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼會害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤卷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.39,0:17:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是膚淺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.32,0:17:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是膚淺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.49,0:17:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  去意識到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是一名小丑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  在那片黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個神情很寂寞的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來讓你露出笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.79,0:17:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大山
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.31,0:17:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是壞透了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音無同學  不是的  請聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是善意的謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.23,0:17:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個由我去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  誰來說點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.84,0:17:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我連他名字都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:17:59.90,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild聯絡通道  B15
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這已經是第幾個了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:18:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  早就沒在數了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.37,0:18:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  輪到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.65,0:18:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你留到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.24,0:18:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你要前進
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.31,0:18:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去的話就給我快點去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我  前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是喜歡他還是討厭他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.18,0:18:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.85,0:18:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guild被爆破後的遺跡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.28,0:18:35.20,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild最底層  爆炸中心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.81,0:18:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡能一口氣下到最底層
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.87,0:18:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音無君和由依去找本體
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦找到  就催促她使用「harmonics」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.94,0:18:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.50,0:18:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向君不是也說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.84,0:18:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她等著的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我來戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.68,0:18:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太弱了  根本不值一提
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請提一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.62,0:18:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.85,0:18:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這如果是最後一次作戰就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.20,0:18:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  由依呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只聽到一聲很短暫的悲鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了天使的犧牲品了嗎  太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.78,0:19:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是馬上就來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.44,0:19:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次活下來的又只有我們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和上次一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該是最後一個了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.32,0:19:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  你別在這裡發呆了  快點去找本體
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.39,0:19:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.38,0:20:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  真難纏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摀住耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guard  Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.59,0:20:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「howling」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.42,0:20:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳朵…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有暈過去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.69,0:20:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.78,0:20:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我塞著耳塞聽不見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  你就死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.40,0:20:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話  就用另一把匕首割破你的喉嚨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.85,0:20:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.29,0:21:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.48,0:21:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.15,0:21:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.05,0:21:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰線的大家都拼上了性命來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.28,0:21:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.66,0:21:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.47,0:21:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點勉強你很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.91,0:21:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是希望你能使用一個能力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.31,0:21:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「harmonics」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你用了大家就能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.32,0:21:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體能受得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.23,0:21:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  只用一次的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guard  Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「harmonics」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好像改寫了程式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.77,0:21:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  一切都會回到她的體內
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.22,0:21:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼多冷酷的我們？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.60,0:21:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.38,0:21:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是分身也有意識
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.66,0:21:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那並不是消失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.75,0:21:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是同化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.35,0:22:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,襲擊你們的眾多的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到她的體內
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次性吸收這麼多的意識
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.71,0:22:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得會沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.88,0:22:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.31,0:22:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.17,0:22:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要平安無事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
